DOC.brief_summary: To demonstrate the relative bioequivalency of comparing single 100 mg doses Of Cord's 50 mg Desipramine Hcl tablets to Merrell Dow's 50 mg Norpramin tablets.
DOC.brief_title: To Demonstrate the Relative Bioequivalency of Comparing Single 100 mg Doses Of Cord's 50 mg Desipramine HCL Tablets To Merrell Dow's 50 mg Norpramin Tablets
DOC.criteria: No clinically significant abnormal finding on physical exam, medical history, or clinical laboratory results on screening. Positive test results for HIV or hepatitis B or C. Treatment for drug or alcohol dependence.
